5d78c0c1d5882.name: Cosy house in the forrest
5d78c0c1d5882.description:
A cosy "hygge" house is for sale at the edge of a forrest. The house is created and designed by the architect Jonas Menso. It's build with glas and wooden components which makes it easily adapt to its surroundings.

Visits are possible every second saturday from 10 - 14.

5d78d8f5c0225.name: Apartement at the beach
5d78d8f5c0225.description:
This 59sqm big apartement is ready for rent close to amager beach. It has a big living room and a build in kitchen. Supermarkets are around the corner and the famous "Juvenus" is 200m away from it.
For visits, you can contact me at 1234123.

5d7b62381a159.name: Svanemøllen President Suite
5d7b62381a159.description: Svanemøllen is know for its special atmosphere. It's close to Copenhagen but still far enough not to have a big city feeling. The strand is also very popular among the danish people. The apartment itself has a nice view over the sea and is equipped with a newly installed "KINGO" kitchen.

5d7b6383836c7.name: Central house in Nørreport
5d7b6383836c7.description: This is a real rarity. Just 100m away from the Nørreport station is a house for sale. It has two floors, 3 bathrooms and two garages for your cars. The house was build in 1968 and renovated in 2016. I.e. from the outside it has it's nice danish touch but the inside is very modern.

5d7b65858085d.name: Cosy hygge apartement 4
5d7b65858085d.description: This small apartment is a real portrayal of the danish hygge term. Located close to the ARos museum it has everything you need. The bathroom has been designed by the danish designer "kLUST" and will make you feel relaxed after a long day of work.

5d7b66a401d46.name: Forest villa
5d7b66a401d46.description: Ever dreamed of your own disney like villa close to Aarhus? Look no further, you found it. This 3 stories house in the middle of the outside forest to Aarhus is the storytale dream. You wouldn't believe what you can do here,

5d7b6c27c55f7.name: Five stories house
5d7b6c27c55f7.description: A pretty two stories house in Copenhagen is for sale. Newly renovated, it has everything you would expect from a house in the 21st century. This neighborhood has been certificated by "Neighborhood Magazine" as one of the best neighborhoods in whole copenhagen!

5d7b7ccbb17c8.name: 2 bedroom apartment
5d7b7ccbb17c8.description: This lovely two bedroom apartment has just been newly build close to Dronning louises bro. It has a nice modern american kitchen and access to rooftop terrace. Since there's a gym in the same building, you get 50% off on a membership as a neighbour!

5d7cead89497c.name: Pretty apartment in Nørrebro
5d7cead89497c.description: This small but pretty apartment is for rent in the heart of Nørrebro. It has everything you need and supermarkets like Netto and Lidl are just around the corner.
